{{ 'custom-cuehealth.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}

<div class="ch-page-hero">
  <div class="ch-page-hero__inner">
    <p class="ch-page-hero__eyebrow">CueHealth Policies</p>
    <h1 class="ch-page-hero__heading">Return & Refund Policy</h1>
    <p class="ch-page-hero__sub">Your satisfaction is our priority. Last updated: May 2026.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="ch-policy-wrapper page-width">
  <div class="ch-policy-content">

    <div class="ch-policy-highlight">
      <span>🔄</span>
      <div>
        <strong>7-Day Easy Returns</strong>
        <p>Not satisfied? Return within 7 days of delivery for a full refund — no questions asked.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2>1. Return Eligibility</h2>
    <p>You can request a return within <strong>7 calendar days</strong> of receiving your order, provided:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>The product is unused and in its original sealed packaging</li>
      <li>All original labels, tags, and seals are intact</li>
      <li>The product is not damaged due to misuse or improper storage</li>
    </ul>
    <p><strong>Non-returnable items:</strong> Opened or partially used products, items purchased during special clearance sales (marked as non-returnable at checkout).</p>

    <h2>2. How to Initiate a Return</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>Contact us within 7 days of delivery via:
        <ul>
          <li>Email: <a href="mailto:hello@cuehealth.in">hello@cuehealth.in</a></li>
          <li>WhatsApp: <a href="https://wa.me/917455918832">7455918832</a></li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li>Share your <strong>order number</strong> and reason for return</li>
      <li>Attach photos of the product and packaging</li>
      <li>Our team will review and approve the return within 24–48 hours</li>
      <li>We will arrange a reverse pickup at no charge to you</li>
    </ol>

    <h2>3. Refund Process</h2>
    <p>Once the returned product is received and inspected, your refund will be processed within <strong>5–7 working days</strong>. Refunds are issued to the original payment method:</p>
    <table class="ch-policy-table">
      <thead>
        <tr><th>Payment Method</th><th>Refund Timeline</th></tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>Credit / Debit Card</td><td>5–7 working days</td></tr>
        <tr><td>UPI / Net Banking</td><td>3–5 working days</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Cash on Delivery</td><td>Bank transfer in 5–7 working days</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Store Credit / Gift Card</td><td>Within 24 hours</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
    <p><em>Note: COD refunds require your bank account details (account number and IFSC code).</em></p>

    <h2>4. Damaged or Defective Products</h2>
    <p>If you receive a <strong>damaged, defective, or incorrect product</strong>, please contact us within <strong>48 hours</strong> of delivery with:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Photos/video of the damaged product and packaging</li>
      <li>Your order number</li>
    </ul>
    <p>We will arrange a <strong>free replacement</strong> or issue a <strong>full refund</strong> — your choice.</p>

    <h2>5. Exchange Policy</h2>
    <p>Direct exchanges are not available. If you wish to exchange a product, please return the original and place a new order. Shipping is free for the new order if your return is approved.</p>

    <h2>6. Cancellations</h2>
    <p>Orders can be cancelled <strong>before dispatch</strong> for a full refund. Once dispatched, cancellations are not possible — please follow the return process above. To cancel, contact us immediately via WhatsApp at 7455918832.</p>

    <div class="ch-policy-contact-bar">
      <p>Need help with a return?</p>
      <div>
        <a href="mailto:hello@cuehealth.in" class="ch-hero__btn ch-hero__btn--primary">Email Us</a>
        <a href="https://wa.me/917455918832" target="_blank" class="ch-hero__btn ch-hero__btn--secondary">WhatsApp</a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Refund Policy Page",
  "tag": "section",
  "class": "ch-policy-section",
  "settings": [],
  "presets": [{ "name": "Refund Policy Page" }]
}
{% endschema %}
